!!【柯林斯英汉双解大词典】

:<div>

spiritual /ˈspɪrɪtjʊəl/

1. ADJ Spiritual means relating to people's thoughts and beliefs, rather than to their bodies and physical surroundings. 精神的 

例： She lived entirely by spiritual values, in a world of poetry and imagination. 她完全靠着精神价值生活在一个诗歌和想像的世界里。 

2. spiritually ADV 精神地 

例： Our whole programme is spiritually oriented but not religious. 我们的整个节目以精神而不是宗教为导向。 

3. ADJ Spiritual means relating to people's religious beliefs. 宗教的 

例： He is the spiritual leader of the world's Catholics. 他是世界天主教的宗教领袖。

</div>

